                <li>Secure and Transparent Payment System.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Ready to Dive Deeper?</h3>
            <p>Explore our <a href="/documentation/introduction/gettingstarted" class="underline">Getting Started</a> guide or discover advanced <a href="/documentation/introduction/features" class="underline">Features</a> to enhance your experience.</p>
